            <h1 class="text-center"> How to Adopt from PAWSter Care</h1>
           <p class="text-center"><br>
                We have very strict protocols in place for adopting out our shelter cats and dogs. 
                These animals have already been through very difficult times. 
                We need to be 100% certain, without a shadow of a doubt, that they will be placed in 
                loving homes.
            </p> <br>
            <div class="row mt-30"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="box14">
                        <img src="../img/protocol1.jpg" alt="" style="border-radius:8px;">
                        <div class="box-content"><br>
                            <h3 class="title">&nbsp;&nbsp;Meet and Greet</h3>
                            <p aria-controls=""class="post">First, you have to visit the shelter to meet your prospective pet. Seeing their cute photos online is different from meeting them in person. This is where you get to see who will tug at your heartstrings and possibly be a new addition to your home.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text_style">1. Meet and Greet</p>
                </div> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="box14">
                        <img src="../img/protocol2.jpg" alt="" style="border-radius:8px;">
                        <div class="box-content"><br>
                            <h3 class="title">&nbsp;&nbsp;Application and Interview</h3>
                            <p class="post">You need to fill up an application form expressing your intent to adopt your chosen cat or dog. You will also be interviewed at least twice to ensure that you and your chosen pet are a good match and you are able to give them a suitable home.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text_style2">2. Application and Interview</p>
                </div> 
           </div>
