                    <div class="box14">
                        <img src="../img/protocol3.jpg" alt="" style="border-radius:8px;">
                        <div class="box-content">br>
                            <h3 class="title">&nbsp;&nbsp;Shelter Visits</h3>
                            <p class="post">You need to make three (3) separate visits to the shelter to spend time with your prospective pet. This is how you know if your chosen r dog is a good fit. It gives you a chance to bond, or if necessary, pick a different pet that will be a better fit for you and your family.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text_style3">3. Shelter Visits</p>
